title: Cafe Ibis
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee shop with a cafe menu including sandwiches, wraps, breakfast food. A few sandwiches can be made vegan. The soup of the day is sometimes vegan. Vegan potato salad with Nayonaise available and tofu can be substituted in sandwiches and wraps. Many coffees are triple certified. Also sells Alternative Baking Company (ABC) cookies. Wi-fi.
